    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>《Office After Hours》(加班惊魂夜) 是一款时长 1-2 小时的轻度恐怖游戏，设定于一个充满怪异与搞笑异常现象的神秘故事中。</strong></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你只想回家。可你为什么还在这？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的老板坚持要你加班，现在你被困在了下班后的办公室里。留心身边的怪事，也许你就能找到回家的路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207300/extras/fc852a0f5c75d8bedf8558f8353b809d.poster.avif?t=1764755581\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207300/extras/fc852a0f5c75d8bedf8558f8353b809d.webm?t=1764755581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >发现异常</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的轮班期间，办公室将不断变化，你将发现大量工作、咖啡，还有运气好的话……办公室宠物。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >逃离过劳地狱</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若要逃出无限解决方案公司，你必须找到能开启新区域的线索，并揭示更多秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能找到所有数字并收集与剧情相关的物品吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207300/extras/cdad97bd6cb3c381a6077fe0dd4539e5.poster.avif?t=1764755581\" width=795 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207300/extras/cdad97bd6cb3c381a6077fe0dd4539e5.webm?t=1764755581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你能逃出去吗？</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    30 个剧情相关的异常</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    总共超过 40 个异常</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >工作时长</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >约 1-2 小时（可能加班）</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >附加内容：Crossovertime 模式✝️🔄⌛</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索7个重大异常 — 其中一个隐藏着4个较小的异常。参照其他异常游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >错过异常不会受到惩罚，只是纯粹的探索和有趣的遭遇。(~15–25分钟)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207300/extras/c60929aa0c27528c7c1c10c4204fa0f4.poster.avif?t=1764755581\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207300/extras/c60929aa0c27528c7c1c10c4204fa0f4.webm?t=1764755581\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
